description:
Today BEYOND the DARKNESS realizes there has been ET Contact: They Are Here with guest Caroline Cory.

Producer and investigator Caroline Cory, who has her own extensive history with the supernatural, takes our listeners on an extraordinary journey thru jaw-dropping stories of individuals from around the world who share similar accounts of extraterrestrial and otherworldly encounters.

Visit her site here: http://www.ET-Contact.com
